ink ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-karuta\/#So_luoc_ve_game_bai_Karuta\" >S\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 game b\u00e0i Karuta<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-karuta\/#Cach_choi_bai_Karuta\" >C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-karuta\/#The_loai_bai_Uta_Garuta\" >Th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u00e0i Uta Garuta<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-karuta\/#Cach_choi_bai_Karuta_the_loai_Iroha_Karuta\" >C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i Iroha Karuta<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-karuta\/#Ve_cach_choi_Hanafuda\" >V\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Hanafuda<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-karuta\/#Su_pho_bien_cua_bai_Karuta\" >S\u1ef1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i Karuta<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-karuta\/#Loi_ket\" >L\u1eddi k\u1ebft<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>Hi\u1ec7n nay, b\u00e0i Karuta \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1eady n\u00ean, <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-bai-karuta\/\">c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta<\/a> c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m, ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 mang t\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">v\u00e0o SV368<\/a> ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xem n\u1ed9i dung c\u00f3 trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau nh\u00e9.\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"So_luoc_ve_game_bai_Karuta\"><\/span><b>S\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 game b\u00e0i Karuta<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Karuta bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. N\u00f3 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c d\u1ecbp l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i, t\u1ee5 h\u1ecdp gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u1edfi <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3. T\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i vui v\u1ebb, nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c, b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef nh\u1eadt v\u1edbi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1ecf, ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng l\u00f2ng b\u00e0n tay v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c nhau. \u1ede tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng m\u1eb7t l\u00e1 b\u00e0i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u1ebd c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, h\u00f3a l\u00e1, th\u01a1 ca, t\u1ee5c ng\u1eef hay l\u00e0 v\u1ebd v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt th\u1eddi x\u01b0a. Trong c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i T\u00e2y th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c qu\u00fd t\u1ed9c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e2y th\u1eddi c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ea1i. Th\u00ec \u1edf b\u00e0i Karuta l\u1ea1i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a 100 v\u1ecb thi nh\u00e2n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3820\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3820\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3820 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-1.jpg\" alt=\"S\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 game b\u00e0i Karuta\" width=\"800\" height=\"395\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-1.jpg?v=1735821825 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-1-300x148.jpg?v=1735821825 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-1-768x379.jpg?v=1735821825 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3820\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u01a1 l\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 game b\u00e0i Karuta<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_choi_bai_Karuta\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong b\u00e0i Karuta kh\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c, bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1<\/span><b> c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn 3 lo\u1ea1i ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Uta Garuta, Hanafuda v\u00e0 Iroha Karuta.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_loai_bai_Uta_Garuta\"><\/span><b>Th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u00e0i Uta Garuta<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Theo nh\u01b0 phi\u00ean \u00e2m ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt th\u00ec Uta c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 b\u00e0i h\u00e1t ho\u1eb7c th\u01a1 c\u1ed5, c\u00f2n Garuta l\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn \u00e2m c\u1ee7a Karuta. N\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u00e0i ng\u00e2m th\u01a1. Tr\u00ean c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e0i th\u01a1 trong t\u1eadp \u201c th\u01a1 tr\u0103m nh\u00e0\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1eadp th\u01a1 n\u00e0y g\u1ed3m 100 b\u00e0i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m theo th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u1ea3n ca d\u00e0i c\u00f3 5 c\u00e2u v\u1edbi 35 \u00e2m ti\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u00e0i kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i nh\u1ea5t, b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edb h\u1ebft t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e2u th\u01a1 c\u1ee7a 100 b\u00e0i.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o tham gia ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i s\u1ebd chia l\u00e0m 2 b\u00ean kh\u00e1c nhau. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i gi\u1eef trong tay to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 h\u1ebft 100 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i Yomifuda, c\u00f2n c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i Torifuda \u0111\u1eb7t ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee7. Khi m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 b\u00e0i Yomifuda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00e2m l\u00ean, th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebb b\u00e0i Torifuda c\u00f3 ghi n\u1eeda sau c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i th\u01a1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3821\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3821\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3821 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-2.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-2.jpg?v=1735821826 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-2-300x188.jpg?v=1735821826 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-2-768x480.jpg?v=1735821826 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3821\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_choi_bai_Karuta_the_loai_Iroha_Karuta\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i Iroha Karuta<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u00e0i c\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Edo v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9ng cho tr\u1ebb em ch\u01a1i. M\u1ed7i b\u1ed9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 96 l\u00e1, trong \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec 48 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in c\u00e1c c\u00e2u t\u1ee5c ng\u1eef (Yomifuda), c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c in h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh k\u00e8m v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u1eef Hiragana n\u1eb1m \u1edf g\u00f3c tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng (Torifuda).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 ch\u01a1i Uta Garuta, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc n\u1eafm h\u1ebft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c l\u00e1 Yomifuda l\u00e0 t\u1ee5c ng\u1eef v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ecdc ra nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i xung quanh s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ra l\u00e1 Torifuda t\u01b0\u1edbng \u1ee9ng, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ee5c ng\u1eef nghe th\u1ea5y. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ra l\u00e1 b\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i. \u0110\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ai s\u1eed h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u l\u00e1 b\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3822\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3822\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3822 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-3.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i Iroha Karuta\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-3.jpg?v=1735821826 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-3-300x188.jpg?v=1735821826 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-3-768x480.jpg?v=1735821826 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3822\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i Iroha Karuta<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ve_cach_choi_Hanafuda\"><\/span><b>V\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i Hanafuda<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi Hanafuda, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi v\u1edbi t\u00ean l\u00e0 b\u00e0i hoa, b\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 in h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng lo\u00e0i hoa, c\u00e2y c\u1ed1i hay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0ng cho 12 th\u00e1ng trong n\u0103m. M\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi 4 l\u00e1 b\u00e0i, c\u00e1c l\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ebd c\u00e1ch \u0111i\u1ec7u theo \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng m\u00f9a. Gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi b\u00e0i T\u00e2y, Hanafuda g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 4 lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nhau l\u00e0 Kasu, Tanzaku, Hikari v\u00e0 Tane.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1eeb 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 ph\u00fat, m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u00f3 12 v\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c \u00edt h\u01a1n t\u00f9y theo nh\u01b0 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi nhau. Khi v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i Hanafuda, kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi 2 lo\u1ea1i b\u00e0i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00eau \u1edf tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cao h\u01a1n th\u00ec gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. S\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng l\u00e1 b\u00e0i b\u1ea1n n\u1eafm trong tay.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Su_pho_bien_cua_bai_Karuta\"><\/span><b>S\u1ef1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i Karuta<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Xem x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y l\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3, b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Ng\u00e0y nay, tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n, nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t n\u00e9t v\u0103n h\u00f3a ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 phim, anime, truy\u1ec7n tranh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng. Ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng, y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n. C\u00e1c l\u00e1 b\u00e0i ch\u0103m ch\u00fat t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n tr\u00ed nh\u1edb, mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3823\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3823\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3823 size-full\" title=\"c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-4.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ef1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i Karuta\" width=\"800\" height=\"478\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-4.jpg?v=1735821827 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-4-300x179.jpg?v=1735821827 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/cach-choi-karuta-4-768x459.jpg?v=1735821827 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3823\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1ef1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i Karuta<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Loi_ket\"><\/span><b>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean bi\u1ebft. Hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh em hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u00e0 tham gia ch\u01a1i vui v\u1ebb h\u01a1n. Theo d\u00f5i SV368 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hi\u1ec7n nay, b\u00e0i Karuta \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1eady n\u00ean, c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i Karuta c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m, ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 mang t\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00e0i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3820,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[94],"class_list":["post-3819","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc","tag-cach-choi-bai-karuta"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3819","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3819"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3819\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5894,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3819\/revisions\/5894"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3820"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3819"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3819"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3819"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}